CLICKING THE SOURCE LINK will bring you to #34 gifs of Eva Mendes (1974) in the film Urban Legends: Final Cut (2000). Please do not repost these gifs in anyway by adding them into gif hunts or distributing them as your own. If you convert them into gif icons and redistribute them, please credit me and link back to this pack. DO NOT use these gifs if you write “taboo themes” or real life/celebrities. You will be blocked. Please like or reblog if you’re going to use these gifs.

In the source link, you will find 78 gifs in 245x150 of LAMORNE MORRIS (1983) in Night Shift (2023). He is of Afro-American descent, so please cast accordingly. All gifs were made from scratch by me and are for roleplay purposes only. Please consider giving this a reblog if using or if you found this to be useful. Do not repost or claim as your own. If you have any questions, feel free to ask!

by following the source link you’ll be directed to #494 gifs of JEFFREY DEAN MORGAN as JACOB KANON in THE POSTCARD KILLINGS (2020). these gifs were made by me from scratch and are not to be added to any gif hunts. please do not resize or use for any taboo content. these can be used for crackships/manip but please credit me. if you’ve found these helpful please like and/or reblog. thanks in advance!

[HERE ] you’ll find 225 gifs of the actor, Benjamin Bratt, from his role in the movie, Mother of the Bride (2024). I hope that these gifs can be useful to someone. You can find my rules here. Suffice it to say that I ask that the time I spent making these be respected and that the fc himself be respected. Please be aware that some of these gifs feature flashing lights, food, alcohol, kissing, and semi nudity. If you found these gifs to be helpful, please like and/or reblog this post. Enjoy!
